      <title>微信小程序1</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F1/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="微信小程序-1"><a href="#微信小程序-1" class="headerlink" title="微信小程序-1"></a>微信小程序-1</h1><h2 id="原生框架的目录结构"><a href="#原生框架的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="原生框架的目录结构"></a>原生框架的目录结构</h2><ul><li><p><strong>pages</strong></p><ul><li><strong>index</strong>：存放首页的页面文件<ul><li><em>index.js</em> ：逻辑</li><li><em>index.json</em>：配置项</li><li><em>index.wxml</em>：便签嵌套</li><li><em>index.wxss</em>：样式</li></ul></li><li><strong>logs</strong>：日志页面相关文件</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>utils</strong>：可要可不要，帮助文档相关JS</p></li><li><p><strong>app.js</strong>：本小程序的入口文件和全局文件</p></li><li><p><strong>app.json</strong>：全局配置文件，如整个项目的标题名称</p></li><li><p><strong>app.wxss</strong>:全局样式文件</p></li><li><p><strong>project.config.json</strong>：基础配置、环境配置</p></li><li><p><strong>sitemap.json</strong>：配置小程序及其页面是否循序被微信索引</p><h2 id="小程序配置文件"><a href="#小程序配置文件" class="headerlink" title="小程序配置文件"></a>小程序配置文件</h2><h3 id="app-json"><a href="#app-json" class="headerlink" title="app.json"></a>app.json</h3><h4 id="“pages”"><a href="#“pages”" class="headerlink" title="“pages”"></a><strong>“pages”</strong></h4><blockquote><p>本小程序有哪些页面<br>一 一对应pages文件夹中的路径 </p></blockquote><h4 id="“window”"><a href="#“window”" class="headerlink" title="“window”"></a><strong>“window”</strong></h4><blockquote><p>定义小程序所有页面的顶部背景颜色、文字颜色定义等</p></blockquote><p>-<em>backgroundTextstyle</em> ：下拉刷新的所展现的文字颜色<br>-<em>navigationBarBackgroundColor</em> ：导航栏背景颜色<br>-<em>navigationBarTitleText</em> ：导航栏标题名称<br>-<em>navigationBarTextstyle</em> ：导航栏文字颜色（<code>black or white</code>）<br>-<em>enablePullDownRefresh</em> ：全局下拉刷新</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enablePullDownRefresh:true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  -<em>backgroundColor</em>  ：下拉刷新页面的背景颜色</p><h4 id="“tabbar”"><a href="#“tabbar”" class="headerlink" title="“tabbar”"></a>“tabbar”</h4><p>类似淘宝底部页面的切换<br>在<code>app.josn</code>中添加：输入tabBar回车自动生成如下代码</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">"tabBar": &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    "list": [&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      "pagePath": ",", //要跳转页面的页面路径</span><br><span class="line">      "text": "text", //标题</span><br><span class="line">      "iconPath": "iconPath", //未选中图标</span><br><span class="line">      "selectedIconPath": "selectedIconPath" //已选中图标</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;]</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;app.josn&gt;</code><br>如何改变此处<strong>标题颜色</strong>？<code>在list的同级下编写</code></p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">"tabBar": &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  "list": [&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;],</span><br><span class="line">  "color":"#0094ff",</span><br><span class="line">  "selectedColor": "#000000"//只能使用16进制</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;app.josn&gt;</code><br>如何改变<strong>相对位置</strong>？</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">"tabBar": &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  "list": [&#123;...&#125;],</span><br><span class="line">  "color":"#0094ff",</span><br><span class="line">  "selectedColor": "#000000",</span><br><span class="line">  "position":"top" //未设置的话默认在bottom，tabbar在顶部时默认不显示图标</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;app.josn&gt;</code></p><h3 id="page-json"><a href="#page-json" class="headerlink" title="page.json"></a>page.json</h3><blockquote><p>独立定义每一个页面的一些属性，如颜色等</p></blockquote><p>page.json用法与app.json中的Windo类似，其他使用参考小程序文档</p><h3 id="sitemap-json"><a href="#sitemap-json" class="headerlink" title="sitemap.json"></a>sitemap.json</h3><blockquote><p>了解即可</p></blockquote><h2 id="模板语法"><a href="#模板语法" class="headerlink" title="模板语法"></a>模板语法</h2><h3 id="数据绑定"><a href="#数据绑定" class="headerlink" title="数据绑定"></a>数据绑定</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">标签</th><th align="center">作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">text</td><td align="center">行内标签，默认不换行</td></tr><tr><td align="left">view</td><td align="center">块级标签，默认换行</td></tr><tr><td align="left">页面中显示的数据放在目标页面/XXX.js的data中</td><td align="center"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>test.js</code></td><td align="center"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// pages/test/test.js</span></span><br><span class="line">Page(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    data: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">msg:<span class="string">"hello!world"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">num:<span class="number">10000</span>,</span><br><span class="line">isBoy:<span class="literal">false</span>，</span><br><span class="line">person&#123;</span><br><span class="line">age:<span class="number">74</span>,</span><br><span class="line">height:<span class="number">145</span>,</span><br><span class="line">weight:<span class="number">45</span>, </span><br><span class="line">name:<span class="string">"小王"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    ischecked:<span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></td><td align="center"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>test.wxml</code></td><td align="center"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><figure class="highlight htmlbars"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--pages/test/test.wxml--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--字符串--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;msg&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--数字类型--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;num&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--bool类型--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span>是否是女同学：</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;isBoy&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--object类型--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;person.age&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;person.height&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;person.weight&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;person.name&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--在标签的属性中使用--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span> <span class="attr">data-num</span>=<span class="string">"</span></span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;num&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag"><span class="string">"</span>&gt;</span>自定义属性<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--使用bool类型充当属性 checked--&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">checkbox</span> <span class="attr">checked</span>=<span class="string">"</span></span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;ischecked&#125;<span class="string">"&gt;&lt;/checkbox&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="template-variable"><span class="string">&lt;/view&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></td><td align="center"></td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
